SummaryContaineruniface_104wzs1665702731233.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wzs1665702731233.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wzs1665702731233.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"wzs1665702731233\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      date as timestamp\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Map dates to timestamps\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"wzs1665702731233__topic_d54485e1_d54486e1_d54487e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wzs1665702731233__p_d54488e1_d54489e1_d54490e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$ODx_PARAMS date as timestamp : on</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">off</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wzs1665702731233__section_qxz_hqm_jcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d281807e63\">Arguments</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"wzs1665702731233__ul_ht4_jqm_jcc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wzs1665702731233__li_d25214e1_d25215e1_d25216e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wzs1665702731233__p_d54494e1_d54495e1_d54496e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">on</code>—dates will be mapped to\n                  timestamps (the default)</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wzs1665702731233__li_d25217e1_d25218e1_d25219e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wzs1665702731233__p_d54497e1_d54498e1_d54499e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">off</code>—dates will not be mapped to\n                  timestamps</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wzs1665702731233__section_y1w_jqm_jcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d281807e88\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wzs1665702731233__p_d54503e1_d54504e1_d54505e1\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">date as timestamp</code> option\n            specifies how dates are mapped.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533600\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533600\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "date as timestamp Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 13, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 date as timestamp Map dates to timestamps USYS$ODx_PARAMS date as timestamp : on | off Arguments on —dates will be mapped to timestamps (the default) off —dates will not be mapped to timestamps Description The date as timestamp option specifies how dates are mapped. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}